data.description: A private oasis in desirable Sherwood Hills neighborhood. Relax and enjoy the peace and quiet anywhere on this property which was designed with privacy in mind. There are privacy hedges, a waterfall/pond/river on the side of the house with raised beds for gardening, and artificial grass in the backyard. Step inside to a freshly painted, tri-level home with a remodeled, open-concept kitchen. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms, including the primary suite and a full, hall bathroom. The lower level includes a bedroom, full bathroom, laundry room and a large bonus room. Lower level has the potential to be made into a separate living space. Sherwood Hills is an amazing neighborhood with wide, quiet streets and lots of evergreens. Conveniently located near amenities, parks, schools and easy highway access yet, every time you step out of your front door you feel like you are camping!
